                    <section id="cr-odoo-support-philosophy" class="philosophy-section">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Our Support Philosophy</h2>
        <div class="philosophy-content">
            <p>
                We believe great support isn’t just about fixing bugs — it’s about **building trust**.
                Our team treats your Odoo system like our own, combining proactive monitoring with transparent communication.
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Proactive, Not Reactive:</strong> We identify issues before they become incidents.</li>
                <li><strong>Transparent Communication:</strong> You always know what’s happening and why.</li>
                <li><strong>Continuous Improvement:</strong> We evolve your ERP along with your business goals.</li>
                <li><strong>Long-Term Partnership:</strong> We grow with your team, not just work for it.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


                    <section id="cr-odoo-support-value" class="value-section">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">What’s Included in Every Odoo Support Plan</h2>
