            <div class="value-item">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-clock"></i>
                <h3>Guaranteed Response Time</h3>
                <p>Every ticket gets acknowledged and prioritized under your SLA agreement.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-item">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-file-circle-check"></i>
                <h3>Ticket Tracking &amp; Reports</h3>
                <p>Real-time ticket dashboard and monthly performance analytics.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-item">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-user-shield"></i>
                <h3>Security &amp; Compliance Checks</h3>
                <p>Regular audits to ensure GDPR, ISO, and data protection compliance.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-item">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-gears"></i>
                <h3>Preventive Maintenance</h3>
                <p>Automatic server health checks, log scans, and module optimizations.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


